WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 4=

01:38.050 --> 01:39.930
While searching for clues,

01:40.180 --> 01:41.290
I unexpectedly learned

01:41.540 --> 01:43.980
the Changs had an old steward
surnamed Jiang.

01:45.130 --> 01:46.050
Five years ago,

01:46.380 --> 01:48.540
the steward retired to his hometown

01:48.770 --> 01:50.290
and took a boy with him.

01:50.540 --> 01:51.570
After much investigation,

01:51.820 --> 01:54.050
at Steward Jiang's grave,

01:54.130 --> 01:56.900
I found Mr. Jiang,
who resembles the late Mr. Chang,

01:57.380 --> 01:58.620
or rather,

01:59.180 --> 02:00.690
the real Chang Ning.

02:04.100 --> 02:04.940
If he's Chang Ning,

02:05.290 --> 02:06.130
who am I?

02:06.660 --> 02:07.886
I also want to know who you are

02:08.293 --> 02:09.410
and why you impersonated me.

02:11.890 --> 02:13.380
My mother died 12 years ago.

02:13.820 --> 02:14.906
You claim to be Chang Ning,

02:15.220 --> 02:16.940
but do you know Mrs. Chang's birthday?

02:17.043 --> 02:18.263
The 16th day of the 11th month.

02:18.360 --> 02:19.380
Where was Mrs. Chang from?

02:19.390 --> 02:20.250
Suzhou.

02:20.260 --> 02:21.160
What was her favorite?

02:21.160 --> 02:22.010
She liked sweets.

02:22.570 --> 02:23.660
Her favorite was

02:23.890 --> 02:25.340
Furong Pastry

02:25.850 --> 02:27.060
from Jiangnan Yipinju.

02:33.130 --> 02:34.850
Under the desk in the study,

02:34.861 --> 02:36.081
there is a character engraved.

02:37.410 --> 02:38.500
What is it?

02:43.850 --> 02:44.850
16 years ago,

02:45.290 --> 02:46.556
my father went to the demon sect

02:46.780 --> 02:48.220
to help Ms. Cai Pingshu.

02:48.730 --> 02:49.783
My mother suddenly fell ill

02:49.850 --> 02:51.463
and accidentally tipped over the stove,

02:51.850 --> 02:53.100
burning my left arm.

02:53.410 --> 02:54.250
Do you have

02:54.410 --> 02:55.250
a scar on your arm?

03:06.570 --> 03:07.410
What's wrong?

03:07.690 --> 03:08.980
Too afraid to show it?

03:09.730 --> 03:11.780
Clearly, he's hiding something.

03:12.260 --> 03:13.500
I suppose everyone knows

03:13.500 --> 03:15.570
who the real one is now.

03:20.260 --> 03:21.940
The Chang residence has been dug up.

03:22.940 --> 03:23.966
Everything was destroyed.

03:24.610 --> 03:26.570
Those with ulterior motives

03:26.690 --> 03:28.076
can surely make up stories at will.

03:29.060 --> 03:29.900
Let me ask you.

03:30.500 --> 03:31.500
On the 3rd shelf, 4th row

03:31.780 --> 03:33.730
of my father's study bookshelf,

03:33.913 --> 03:34.913
there's also a character.

03:35.730 --> 03:36.780
What is it?

03:39.840 --> 03:41.290
A dog once bit me when I was little,

03:41.780 --> 03:42.800
leaving a scar on my calf.

03:43.730 --> 03:45.130
Do you dare roll up your pants

03:45.610 --> 03:46.450
so everyone can see?

03:46.980 --> 03:47.820
Nonsense.

03:48.260 --> 03:49.380
There is no scar.

03:49.690 --> 03:50.530
Indeed.

03:50.940 --> 03:53.570
It's your story against mine.

03:54.170 --> 03:56.660
All of you here are respected figures.

03:56.820 --> 03:58.850
Yet you've fallen
into this trap of self-proof.

04:00.220 --> 04:01.220
If so,

04:01.380 --> 04:02.340
why not fight

04:02.570 --> 04:05.100
with your family's Willow Sword?

04:05.380 --> 04:06.220
This swordsmanship

04:06.540 --> 04:07.610
can't be faked, right?

04:10.570 --> 04:11.540
As you wish.

04:12.010 --> 04:12.850
Lord Qi,

04:13.060 --> 04:14.010
you knew my father well.

04:14.180 --> 04:15.880
You know I've been sickly
since childhood,

04:16.100 --> 04:17.610
only practicing internal cultivation

04:17.610 --> 04:18.563
to strengthen meridians,

04:18.596 --> 04:19.896
unable to train in swordsmanship.

04:20.020 --> 04:20.860
That's why my father

04:21.100 --> 04:22.340
kept me away from Jianghu,

04:22.610 --> 04:23.576
never letting me go out.

04:24.370 --> 04:25.210
Lord Song,

04:25.700 --> 04:26.900
if you intend to play a trick,

04:27.220 --> 04:28.370
at least take it seriously

04:28.610 --> 04:30.610
and pick someone
skilled in martial arts.

04:30.810 --> 04:31.780
This way,

04:32.370 --> 04:33.676
you're only humiliating yourself.

04:33.980 --> 04:34.820
You...

04:35.340 --> 04:36.290
As everyone knows,

04:36.290 --> 04:38.140
Ning has been sickly since childhood.

04:38.410 --> 04:40.020
It is understandable that Mr. Chang

04:40.020 --> 04:41.340
did not teach him martial arts.

04:43.170 --> 04:44.010
Xiuming,

04:44.370 --> 04:45.780
you know Chang Haosheng well,

04:45.930 --> 04:47.490
and you treated his injuries.

04:47.730 --> 04:48.610
Speak up.

04:48.900 --> 04:49.740
Who is real?

04:49.980 --> 04:50.820
Lord Song,

04:51.100 --> 04:51.980
you found the person.

04:52.900 --> 04:54.170
I only treat injuries.

04:54.930 --> 04:56.850
I don't care who he is.

04:57.290 --> 04:59.050
- You...
- My father just passed.

04:59.290 --> 05:00.490
Instead of seeking the culprit,

05:00.930 --> 05:02.250
you found a man

05:02.250 --> 05:03.370
resembling my father

05:03.980 --> 05:06.050
and put on such a show.

05:06.730 --> 05:08.100
What do you want?

05:08.370 --> 05:09.810
Who'd act with you?

05:09.850 --> 05:10.690
Enough.

05:12.170 --> 05:13.220
This is serious.

05:13.610 --> 05:14.850
Since it's hard to tell,

05:15.100 --> 05:16.490
let me test

05:16.810 --> 05:18.850
their internal cultivation.

05:20.540 --> 05:21.380
Uncle Li,

05:21.826 --> 05:22.740
that requires injecting

05:22.740 --> 05:24.050
internal energy into meridians.

05:24.610 --> 05:25.540
Isn't that too harsh?

05:27.100 --> 05:27.940
Yunke?

05:30.220 --> 05:31.340
Zhao is right.

05:32.610 --> 05:34.730
Don't harm the real Ning.

05:57.170 --> 05:58.010
Uncle Li,

05:58.021 --> 05:59.500
Chang Ning's injuries are not healed.

05:59.511 --> 06:00.850
At this rate, he may die.

06:01.850 --> 06:03.220
Their true energy

06:03.580 --> 06:05.540
was cultivated
with the Changs' techniques.

06:12.610 --> 06:13.810
Their meridians are damaged.

06:13.930 --> 06:14.883
Their lives are at risk.

06:15.490 --> 06:16.330
Yunke,

06:16.580 --> 06:18.340
let me take them back to heal.

06:18.700 --> 06:19.606
Examine them tomorrow.

06:37.980 --> 06:38.820
He's fine.

06:39.540 --> 06:40.380
He'll wake up soon.

06:41.780 --> 06:42.660
You don't care

06:43.020 --> 06:44.340
who the real one is?

06:44.810 --> 06:45.700
As I said,

06:46.220 --> 06:47.250
I only treat illnesses.

06:52.780 --> 06:54.900
That's Breeze, my father's favorite.

06:57.100 --> 06:58.780
Drinks in spring

07:00.140 --> 07:03.580
last ten years.

07:07.610 --> 07:08.490
Since you know

07:08.490 --> 07:09.850
so many family secrets,

07:10.660 --> 07:12.290
you must be close to Chang.

07:14.540 --> 07:15.380
Tomorrow,

07:16.290 --> 07:17.410
if there's more to say,

07:17.980 --> 07:18.930
think it through first,

07:19.810 --> 07:20.780
or you two

07:21.290 --> 07:22.290
may not end well.

07:43.730 --> 07:44.570
Zhao,

07:44.700 --> 07:46.050
why hold an empty bowl?

07:46.490 --> 07:47.370
Craving meat?

07:50.140 --> 07:51.780
I want wonton.

07:52.140 --> 07:52.980
Zhao,

07:53.540 --> 07:54.540
does the collarbone hurt

07:55.020 --> 07:56.490
when pierced?

07:57.020 --> 07:57.860
Of course,

07:58.410 --> 07:59.340
why ask that?

08:00.290 --> 08:01.930
I just went to the kitchen for food.

08:02.490 --> 08:03.810
Zhuang Shu said

08:04.410 --> 08:05.250
that tomorrow,

08:05.340 --> 08:06.610
if no conclusion is reached,

08:06.900 --> 08:07.740
Uncle Li

08:07.930 --> 08:10.020
will lock their collarbones,

08:10.257 --> 08:11.456
crippling their martial arts,

08:11.580 --> 08:12.613
to prevent future trouble.

08:37.770 --> 08:38.610
Zhuo...

08:39.980 --> 08:40.820
Yuzhi.

08:46.300 --> 08:47.140
Sleeping drug.

09:19.700 --> 09:20.540
Chang Ning!

09:33.060 --> 09:33.900
Bring the crossbow.

09:59.770 --> 10:01.340
Why pull me down?

10:03.300 --> 10:04.490
Didn't you come here

10:04.820 --> 10:06.220
to leave with me?

10:06.580 --> 10:07.420
Your leaving

10:07.770 --> 10:09.100
will only prove you're a spy.

10:09.850 --> 10:10.690
When you're wanted,

10:10.730 --> 10:11.730
how will you survive?

10:12.100 --> 10:13.420
I'm already doomed.

10:14.301 --> 10:15.478
If I can't avenge while alive,

10:15.489 --> 10:16.329
death is better.

10:16.530 --> 10:17.380
Don't you know

10:17.380 --> 10:18.420
what they will do to me?

10:19.940 --> 10:20.780
Capture the assassin!

10:23.770 --> 10:24.940
We are not assassins.

10:26.100 --> 10:28.010
You must be from Taichu Temple.

10:28.530 --> 10:30.300
We are from Qingque Sect.

10:35.260 --> 10:38.860
(Qiu Yuanfeng, Lord of Taichu Temple)

10:38.980 --> 10:40.580
You must be here

10:40.940 --> 10:42.610
to attend the memorial, right?

10:43.133 --> 10:44.569
(Wang Yuanjing)
Such a long journey

10:44.580 --> 10:45.420
must be exhausting.

10:45.530 --> 10:47.340
Did you really get here by accident?

10:48.940 --> 10:49.780
Yes.

10:50.940 --> 10:52.010
A misunderstanding.

10:53.220 --> 10:54.060
Originally...

11:00.490 --> 11:01.330
Chang Ning!

11:05.130 --> 11:05.970
Chang Ning.

11:07.980 --> 11:08.820
Lord Qiu,

11:09.130 --> 11:10.730
he's a fugitive from Qingque Sect.

11:11.260 --> 11:12.360
Please let me take him away.

11:13.650 --> 11:14.490
Who are you?

11:14.770 --> 11:16.220
Why did you attack me?

11:17.100 --> 11:18.980
You're the one who raided Chang Fort

11:19.650 --> 11:21.300
and killed my father.

11:26.010 --> 11:27.340
An impostor's words

11:27.420 --> 11:28.370
are not credible.

11:31.770 --> 11:33.220
I'm the killer?

11:34.300 --> 11:35.140
Where's the evidence?

11:35.420 --> 11:37.300
When my father escorted me out,

11:38.220 --> 11:40.300
he fought one of the assassins
for a long time.

11:46.420 --> 11:48.490
His attacks had a sandalwood fragrance,

11:49.220 --> 11:50.130
the same

11:50.340 --> 11:51.980
as Lord Qiu carries.

11:53.300 --> 11:54.370
Nonsense.

11:54.890 --> 11:56.530
Taichu Temple is so close to Chang Fort.

11:57.250 --> 11:59.010
Yet they knew nothing

11:59.220 --> 12:00.140
of the great commotion

12:00.220 --> 12:01.490
in Chang Fort?

12:02.940 --> 12:03.780
Indeed.

12:06.490 --> 12:07.980
I wasn't at the temple back then.

12:08.680 --> 12:09.530
Moreover,

12:09.530 --> 12:11.010
Chang Fort had been hidden

12:11.370 --> 12:12.763
in the mountains for over a decade,

12:13.130 --> 12:14.850
cut off from the outside world.

12:15.130 --> 12:16.530
As for the fragrance,

12:17.180 --> 12:18.020
Yuanjing,

12:18.340 --> 12:20.060
please explain to everyone.

12:24.820 --> 12:25.660
Lord Qi,

12:25.850 --> 12:27.850
this incense is our special Ethereal,

12:28.220 --> 12:30.610
crafted with rosewood and Qiong flowers.

12:30.820 --> 12:31.730
It calms energy

12:31.730 --> 12:32.570
and aids cultivation.

12:32.630 --> 12:33.490
Many practitioners

12:33.490 --> 12:34.330
sought it.

12:34.850 --> 12:37.220
Mr. Chang's suspicion of Yuanfeng

12:37.340 --> 12:38.820
was just youthful ignorance.

12:38.940 --> 12:40.010
What Mr. Chang?

12:40.420 --> 12:41.610
He is clearly an unknown spy,

12:41.610 --> 12:43.010
stirring discord.

12:43.700 --> 12:45.220
Lord Qiu, you appear clean.

12:45.770 --> 12:46.836
You only got your position

12:47.180 --> 12:49.820
after Mr. Wu Yuanying's death,

12:49.980 --> 12:53.060
yet you expelled
his beloved Luo Yuanrong...

12:53.060 --> 12:53.900
Nonsense.

12:54.010 --> 12:54.956
How dare you smear me?

12:56.650 --> 12:58.370
Such a schemer

12:59.010 --> 13:00.340
should be executed.

13:00.940 --> 13:01.780
Wait.

13:12.700 --> 13:14.210
Pingchun, Xiaofeng,

13:14.370 --> 13:15.210
you're back.

13:15.386 --> 13:16.685
When we were about to come back,

13:16.730 --> 13:18.123
we met Mr. Jiang at the cliff base.

13:18.890 --> 13:19.890
Mr. Jiang said

13:20.420 --> 13:21.610
Ning is in trouble

13:21.940 --> 13:23.046
and asked us to take him up.

13:23.180 --> 13:24.030
Mr. Jiang,

13:24.060 --> 13:25.180
Lord Qi is also here.

13:25.490 --> 13:26.330
Tell us

13:26.700 --> 13:28.100
everything you know.

13:28.730 --> 13:29.769
He is the real Chang Ning.

13:37.890 --> 13:38.730
Fraud!

13:44.060 --> 13:45.130
Was this from Father?

13:48.130 --> 13:49.220
I'll distract them.

13:49.900 --> 13:51.086
You take the chance to leave.

13:52.180 --> 13:55.220
We are actually both Changs.

13:56.890 --> 13:57.730
What do you mean?

13:59.850 --> 14:01.730
His mother is Mrs. Chang;

14:02.340 --> 14:03.340
my mother

14:03.770 --> 14:04.890
was just a village girl

14:04.890 --> 14:06.410
who had a brief affair with Mr. Chang.

14:07.150 --> 14:08.180
Because of my lowly birth,

14:08.649 --> 14:10.486
I was treated
as Steward Jiang's adopted son,

14:10.820 --> 14:11.660
so I felt resentful.

14:12.340 --> 14:15.010
That day at the grave, I met Lord Song

14:15.420 --> 14:17.220
and learning of the Changs' tragedy.

14:17.220 --> 14:18.610
Then I decided to take his place.

14:19.730 --> 14:21.850
You didn't say that before.

14:22.060 --> 14:23.340
You said

14:23.340 --> 14:24.610
you'd avenge your father.

14:24.700 --> 14:25.700
That's true.

14:26.060 --> 14:27.610
Though Mr. Chang disowned me,

14:27.980 --> 14:28.980
he was still my father.

14:29.420 --> 14:30.340
He was killed,

14:30.610 --> 14:31.530
and I must avenge him.

14:31.850 --> 14:32.690
Nonsense.

14:33.580 --> 14:34.490
Both of you

14:34.770 --> 14:36.820
are still suspicious.

14:37.530 --> 14:38.370
Qi,

14:39.010 --> 14:40.130
Xiaofeng and I found

14:40.130 --> 14:40.980
the Changs' belongings

14:41.363 --> 14:42.829
at a pawnshop near Hanhai Mountains.

14:43.130 --> 14:43.970
Following the clues,

14:44.133 --> 14:45.306
we infiltrated the demon sect

14:45.700 --> 14:47.700
and discovered the culprit
is the Demonic Camp.

14:48.250 --> 14:50.123
We learned that over a year ago,

14:50.134 --> 14:51.707
the demon sect had an internal conflict,

14:52.530 --> 14:54.490
the young master Mu Qingyan was killed,

14:54.490 --> 14:55.340
and Nie Zhe

14:55.340 --> 14:56.580
secured the leader position.

14:57.820 --> 14:59.700
Lately, they've expanded their followers

14:59.700 --> 15:00.753
and trained death squads,

15:00.890 --> 15:02.610
likely targeting
the Six Sects of Beichen,

15:03.706 --> 15:04.866
planning large-scale revenge.

15:08.490 --> 15:09.330
Alright.

15:09.610 --> 15:10.850
Now, the truth is clear.

15:12.420 --> 15:13.260
For safety,

15:13.770 --> 15:14.730
both of you

15:15.130 --> 15:16.250
should stay here.

15:16.730 --> 15:17.850
As for revenge,

15:18.370 --> 15:19.580
after the memorial,

15:19.940 --> 15:20.780
the Six Sects

15:21.010 --> 15:22.340
will give you an answer.

15:28.420 --> 15:29.260
Thank you, Lord Qi.

15:32.420 --> 15:33.340
Since you can't leave,

15:34.100 --> 15:35.820
Mr. Jiang, why not stay

15:36.370 --> 15:37.490
and help with my herb fields,

15:37.890 --> 15:39.940
as a way to strengthen your health?

15:54.490 --> 15:55.370
You've left.

15:56.490 --> 15:57.770
Why get involved?

15:58.350 --> 15:59.600
I didn't know Father's plan

16:00.010 --> 16:01.300
and almost endangered you.

16:03.370 --> 16:04.210
Sorry.

16:09.300 --> 16:10.250
Your survival

16:10.730 --> 16:12.980
is the greatest comfort

16:14.300 --> 16:15.300
to Mr. Chang's spirit.

16:20.890 --> 16:21.730
Is the culprit

16:22.490 --> 16:24.130
really the Demonic Camp?

16:25.380 --> 16:26.610
Not only them.

16:28.820 --> 16:30.490
Qiu Yuanfeng is also involved.

16:31.060 --> 16:32.420
Taichu Temple...

16:34.300 --> 16:35.770
I'll avenge the Changs.

16:37.700 --> 16:38.540
Don't act recklessly.

16:39.060 --> 16:40.010
Neither should you.

16:51.980 --> 16:53.580
As the lord of a temple,

16:54.010 --> 16:56.130
Qiu Yuanfeng ranks in the top ten
among the elites.

16:56.820 --> 16:58.100
Targeting him is suicide.

16:58.643 --> 17:00.016
Master will investigate thoroughly.

17:00.220 --> 17:01.300
You and Mr. Jiang

17:01.420 --> 17:03.370
should just stay here.

17:03.980 --> 17:04.820
Zhao, don't worry.

17:05.180 --> 17:06.193
The Peng bird is injured;

17:06.490 --> 17:07.330
I can't leave either.

17:07.677 --> 17:09.210
The Golden Peng recognizes its master.

17:09.660 --> 17:10.940
How could it obey you?

17:13.980 --> 17:15.810
My father raised it.

17:17.570 --> 17:19.050
I heard from Mother

17:19.980 --> 17:21.526
that Uncle Chang had a harsh childhood

17:22.140 --> 17:23.330
with scarce food.

17:24.290 --> 17:25.730
How could he have raised a Peng bird?

17:28.050 --> 17:28.890
Zhao.

17:39.380 --> 17:40.420
Why don't you ask

17:41.770 --> 17:42.610
who I really am?

17:43.956 --> 17:45.929
Jiang Ning fabricated an identity
to protect you.

17:46.980 --> 17:48.700
Uncle Chang taught you his martial arts

17:48.860 --> 17:49.810
without reservation,

17:50.570 --> 17:52.420
even risking his life to protect you.

17:52.900 --> 17:54.160
I'm sure they had their reasons.

17:55.420 --> 17:57.010
You must be someone they trust.

17:59.220 --> 18:00.060
They trust you;

18:00.980 --> 18:01.820
I trust them.

18:03.010 --> 18:04.810
I don't know your real name yet,

18:06.140 --> 18:07.530
so I'll treat you as Chang Ning.

18:08.140 --> 18:09.700
As long as you do nothing evil,

18:10.290 --> 18:11.330
I'll protect you

18:11.900 --> 18:13.420
and keep you out of danger.

18:22.896 --> 18:24.220
Zhao, you don't need to follow me.

18:24.220 --> 18:25.376
I'm just going to Herb Hut,

18:25.620 --> 18:26.780
not to confront Qiu Yuanfeng

18:26.910 --> 18:27.870
or the demon sect.

18:31.250 --> 18:32.380
This involves the demon sect.

18:32.660 --> 18:34.250
The Six Sects will surely unite,

18:34.330 --> 18:35.170
cooperating fully.

18:35.380 --> 18:36.330
Perhaps by now,

18:36.377 --> 18:37.816
they're already making arrangements,

18:37.860 --> 18:38.810
carrying out their duty.

18:47.420 --> 18:48.290
Truly,

18:48.980 --> 18:50.140
working together

18:50.770 --> 18:51.860
against a common enemy.

18:55.140 --> 18:56.900
How affectionate.

18:57.620 --> 18:59.250
So, it's Zhao

18:59.490 --> 19:00.900
and Chang.

19:02.180 --> 19:04.180
The young master of Peiqiong Manor

19:04.180 --> 19:05.940
is about to arrive.

19:06.140 --> 19:06.980
Zhao,

19:07.570 --> 19:09.620
don't forget your betrothal,

19:09.860 --> 19:11.140
to avoid gossip.

19:17.980 --> 19:19.290
You didn't know?

19:19.810 --> 19:21.700
Zhao is engaged.

19:21.980 --> 19:24.490
Their families are old friends.

19:24.860 --> 19:27.090
The young master, Zhou Yuqi,

19:27.090 --> 19:27.980
and Zhao

19:28.050 --> 19:29.810
are childhood sweethearts,

19:29.810 --> 19:31.220
a perfect match.

19:31.490 --> 19:32.330
Zhao,

19:32.420 --> 19:34.140
why didn't you tell Chang

19:34.330 --> 19:35.700
so he

19:35.700 --> 19:37.180
wouldn't stay

19:37.330 --> 19:38.420
with another man's fiancée?

19:40.570 --> 19:42.050
Do you hear me?

19:43.570 --> 19:44.940
I was looking for Yuzhi.

19:44.980 --> 19:47.490
His fiancée stays with another man.

19:47.620 --> 19:48.460
Yuzhi

19:48.530 --> 19:49.810
is so broad-minded.

19:50.250 --> 19:51.090
You...

19:51.250 --> 19:52.090
Zhao,

19:52.290 --> 19:53.130
that's nonsense.

19:53.130 --> 19:54.500
Exactly, nonsense!

19:59.050 --> 20:00.250
Yuqi

20:00.660 --> 20:02.290
is Zhao's fiancé.

20:03.180 --> 20:04.620
When her training ends,

20:05.090 --> 20:07.130
she'll become the young mistress
of Peiqiong Manor.

20:09.290 --> 20:10.220
I heard

20:10.770 --> 20:13.050
Lord Zhou and your aunt
were once engaged,

20:13.730 --> 20:15.490
but he married someone else.

20:16.220 --> 20:18.140
Won't your families have resentment?

20:18.570 --> 20:20.050
What resentment?

20:20.490 --> 20:22.900
My aunt arranged that marriage.

20:23.180 --> 20:24.290
Then why did your aunt

20:24.570 --> 20:26.010
accept this marriage?

20:30.530 --> 20:31.370
Take the medicine.

20:36.570 --> 20:37.860
What kind of person

20:38.660 --> 20:39.500
is Zhou Yuqi?

20:41.570 --> 20:42.530
A refined gentleman,

20:43.140 --> 20:44.010
kind and warm,

20:44.700 --> 20:45.620
nice and friendly,

20:46.162 --> 20:47.281
pleasant as a spring breeze.

20:55.250 --> 20:56.330
Chang,

20:56.570 --> 20:57.730
my Smiley!

21:08.660 --> 21:10.090
Run, run, run!

21:11.770 --> 21:12.610
Don't come over!

21:15.380 --> 21:16.250
Zhao.

21:19.020 --> 21:22.420
(Zhou Yuqi, Min Xinrou, Peiqiong Manor)

21:25.330 --> 21:26.290
Yuqi.

21:26.490 --> 21:27.330
Long time no see.

21:27.770 --> 21:28.610
Long time no see.

21:29.290 --> 21:30.130
Why are you here?

21:30.730 --> 21:32.330
I collected many rare items

21:33.010 --> 21:34.730
and came early

21:35.010 --> 21:35.850
with Father

21:36.700 --> 21:37.900
to give them to you.

21:41.180 --> 21:42.020
Yuqi,

21:42.730 --> 21:44.380
where's the big kite you promised me?

21:44.420 --> 21:45.980
Xinrou has made it for you.

21:46.010 --> 21:46.850
It's there.

21:47.900 --> 21:49.130
Han, come with me.

21:55.180 --> 21:56.020
Do you like it?

22:04.250 --> 22:05.090
Yuqi,

22:05.900 --> 22:07.460
this is Chang Ning.

22:07.860 --> 22:08.700
Ning,

22:10.810 --> 22:12.420
I was deeply saddened to hear

22:12.420 --> 22:13.260
about the massacre.

22:13.770 --> 22:14.610
Ning,

22:14.621 --> 22:15.760
please accept my condolences.

22:15.810 --> 22:16.810
My father has passed,

22:17.936 --> 22:19.242
and injustice remains unresolved.

22:19.390 --> 22:20.390
No need

22:20.530 --> 22:21.370
for empty sympathy.

22:26.010 --> 22:27.676
My father and Mr. Chang
were old friends.

22:27.940 --> 22:28.840
I especially brought

22:29.140 --> 22:30.810
a Warm Jade Qilin,

22:30.821 --> 22:32.409
conducive to cultivating internal power.

22:32.420 --> 22:33.420
Perfect for Ning.

22:49.660 --> 22:51.860
Then I'll thank you on his behalf.

22:51.980 --> 22:52.820
No need.

22:59.420 --> 23:00.260
What's this?

23:01.010 --> 23:02.290
Xinrou made this hairpin

23:02.490 --> 23:03.876
with mermaid tears for your mother.

23:03.900 --> 23:05.010
I heard she already had one,

23:05.490 --> 23:06.330
so this makes a pair.

23:07.070 --> 23:08.380
You're so thoughtful.

23:09.420 --> 23:10.260
And this?

23:10.810 --> 23:12.700
These are rare storybooks
collected by Xinrou.

23:13.220 --> 23:14.273
Many are unique copies.

23:15.530 --> 23:16.860
I was worried about that.

23:17.530 --> 23:18.720
Xinrou, thank you.

23:19.090 --> 23:19.930
We're family.

23:20.140 --> 23:20.980
No need for thanks.

23:34.180 --> 23:35.020
Chang Ning,

23:35.330 --> 23:36.810
why throw a tantrum?

23:37.220 --> 23:38.646
Are you going to listen to your aunt

23:38.810 --> 23:39.940
and marry Zhou Yuqi?

23:40.490 --> 23:41.396
What's wrong with that?

23:41.490 --> 23:42.710
What if he's not right for you?

23:43.010 --> 23:44.570
I can remarry.

23:45.140 --> 23:45.980
Not a big deal.

23:46.420 --> 23:47.770
Marriage is serious.

23:48.860 --> 23:50.330
Your aunt is gone.

23:50.730 --> 23:51.700
If you don't like it,

23:52.620 --> 23:53.733
you can break the betrothal.

23:55.330 --> 23:56.900
Marrying Yuqi is quite good.

23:57.660 --> 23:59.050
Peiqiong Manor is beautiful,

23:59.050 --> 24:00.010
the town is bustling,

24:00.660 --> 24:02.380
and the surrounding cities and towns

24:02.380 --> 24:03.220
have everything.

24:03.420 --> 24:04.730
It's livelier than Luoying Valley.

24:05.770 --> 24:07.530
Yuqi has treated me well
since childhood.

24:08.980 --> 24:10.140
After marriage,

24:10.940 --> 24:13.220
Peiqiong Manor will be mine.

24:19.730 --> 24:21.730
Chang Ning, what are you scheming?

24:22.143 --> 24:23.869
(Determination and Force)
Look at yourself.

24:24.220 --> 24:25.330
Think it about it.

24:25.516 --> 24:26.900
Marriage is not for you to decide.

24:26.900 --> 24:27.740
Chang Ning.

24:28.700 --> 24:30.420
I'm too young to get married.

24:30.860 --> 24:32.250
Moreover, Grandfather is ill...

24:32.570 --> 24:34.290
He is cared for by the Huangsha gang.

24:34.530 --> 24:35.380
You need not worry.

24:35.513 --> 24:37.180
(Yang Heying)
Marrying into Guangtian Sect

24:37.180 --> 24:39.082
(Sha, Lady of Siqi Sect)
is a rare opportunity.

24:39.093 --> 24:40.860
Why are you so ungrateful?

24:40.860 --> 24:41.700
I...

24:41.700 --> 24:42.810
You are my daughter.

24:43.010 --> 24:44.140
You must obey me.

24:44.980 --> 24:46.570
This is settled; no more discussion.

24:48.490 --> 24:50.250
This is Lord Yang of Siqi Sect.

25:21.010 --> 25:21.900
What does he

25:22.700 --> 25:23.980
want again?

26:27.730 --> 26:28.570
Zhao.

26:30.180 --> 26:31.700
Did you just see an old woman?

26:31.940 --> 26:32.980
What old woman?

26:33.660 --> 26:34.730
You must've been mistaken.

26:35.140 --> 26:36.330
In the dead of night,

26:37.330 --> 26:38.620
what are you doing here?

26:39.460 --> 26:40.660
(Breeze)

26:41.700 --> 26:42.540
Breeze.

26:42.900 --> 26:44.140
Zhao, do you want to try it?

26:45.140 --> 26:46.240
Your wounds aren't healed.

26:46.980 --> 26:47.900
How can you drink?

26:54.300 --> 26:55.660
(Breeze)

26:55.660 --> 26:56.980
(Why is one jar missing?)

27:01.260 --> 27:04.700
(Breeze)

27:13.620 --> 27:14.460
Father,

27:14.620 --> 27:15.460
Mother,

27:15.700 --> 27:16.730
do you think someone

27:16.730 --> 27:17.770
would steal wine here?

27:18.010 --> 27:19.180
Steal wine?

27:20.530 --> 27:21.420
Of course.

27:21.810 --> 27:23.010
Your aunt has stolen before.

27:23.620 --> 27:24.810
My aunt had such a habit?

27:24.860 --> 27:25.700
Yes.

27:26.330 --> 27:27.180
Your aunt

27:27.730 --> 27:29.250
loved the wine brewed by Lei.

27:29.810 --> 27:30.650
But the ingredients

27:31.220 --> 27:32.490
were rare,

27:32.900 --> 27:34.420
and Lei was reluctant to give more.

27:35.490 --> 27:37.140
So, she went to the wine cellar

27:37.490 --> 27:38.980
with Wu and Yuanrong to steal some.

27:39.180 --> 27:40.020
Is the wine

27:40.180 --> 27:41.220
Breeze?

27:42.110 --> 27:42.950
Come on.

27:42.980 --> 27:43.980
Let's drink.

27:43.990 --> 27:44.850
- Come on.
- Cheers!

27:44.860 --> 27:45.980
- Cheers!
- Come on.

27:46.090 --> 27:46.930
Cheers!

27:47.010 --> 27:48.530
Breeze!

27:49.580 --> 27:51.840
♪In the martial world♪

27:52.020 --> 27:54.360
♪With a shining cup♪

27:54.580 --> 27:56.510
♪I drink with delight tonight♪

27:57.090 --> 27:58.370
♪Free to wander♪

27:58.370 --> 28:00.780
♪In the world♪

28:00.780 --> 28:02.140
(Luo Yuanrong, Taichu Temple)

28:02.220 --> 28:06.180
(Wu Yuanying, Taichu Temple)

28:08.090 --> 28:09.330
Come on.

28:09.330 --> 28:10.170
Here.

28:11.570 --> 28:12.490
Yes, it's Breeze.

28:13.700 --> 28:14.730
That's history.

28:16.140 --> 28:16.980
Unfortunately,

28:17.490 --> 28:18.810
those who drank with us then

28:20.090 --> 28:21.090
are all gone,

28:21.980 --> 28:23.010
even Yuanrong

28:24.620 --> 28:25.770
has disappeared.

28:34.180 --> 28:37.300
(Spirit Tablet of Founder Beichen)

29:12.940 --> 29:13.780
Great-aunt.

29:13.780 --> 29:15.593
(Abbess Jingyuan,
Abbess of Xuankong Nunnery)

29:17.660 --> 29:18.500
Abbess Jingyuan.

29:24.586 --> 29:25.759
(Zhou Zhizhen, Peiqiong Manor)

29:25.770 --> 29:26.610
Uncle Zhou.

29:42.980 --> 29:44.500
Lord Yang of Siqi Sect.

29:45.140 --> 29:45.980
Strike the bell.

30:06.250 --> 30:07.090
Zhao,

30:07.290 --> 30:08.490
why strike the bronze bell

30:09.050 --> 30:10.490
before the memorial?

30:15.450 --> 30:16.290
This is impressive.

30:16.290 --> 30:17.130
Indeed.

30:17.140 --> 30:18.040
Impressive.

30:18.250 --> 30:19.090
Yes.

30:22.490 --> 30:23.796
The bell was left by the Founder,

30:24.180 --> 30:25.220
cast from underwater iron.

30:25.530 --> 30:26.720
Ordinary people can't ring it.

30:26.731 --> 30:27.713
As expected of Lord Yang.

30:27.724 --> 30:28.640
Officially, it informs

30:28.730 --> 30:30.220
the gods from all directions.

30:30.900 --> 30:32.730
In fact, it intimidates
the martial world:

30:33.380 --> 30:34.380
Without this skill,

30:34.490 --> 30:36.490
don't envy the status of the Six Sects.

30:38.540 --> 30:39.380
Lord Song

30:39.380 --> 30:40.220
of Guangtian Sect.

30:40.570 --> 30:41.410
Strike the bell.

31:00.570 --> 31:01.810
Lord Song is impressive.

31:02.050 --> 31:03.900
His internal force penetrates the bell.

31:09.010 --> 31:10.250
Truly amazing.

31:15.570 --> 31:16.420
Lord Qiu

31:16.420 --> 31:17.260
of Taichu Temple.

31:17.700 --> 31:18.540
Strike the bell.

31:57.490 --> 31:58.730
12 moves from one palm.

32:00.090 --> 32:00.930
12 moves.

32:03.180 --> 32:04.530
There's always

32:04.820 --> 32:05.660
someone better.

32:05.660 --> 32:06.860
As expected of Lord Qiu.

32:07.330 --> 32:08.940
Lord Qiu is peerless.

32:09.290 --> 32:11.050
Not inferior
to the late Ms. Cai Pingshu.

32:11.090 --> 32:11.940
Indeed.

32:11.940 --> 32:13.090
We are enlightened.

32:13.980 --> 32:14.820
You flatter me.

32:15.810 --> 32:16.650
I dare not

32:16.940 --> 32:19.330
compare myself to Ms. Cai.

32:20.140 --> 32:22.530
But I never slack,

32:23.010 --> 32:23.980
practicing day and night,

32:25.220 --> 32:27.700
only to uphold our reputation

32:28.620 --> 32:30.770
and restore our prestige.

32:31.490 --> 32:32.980
Lord Qiu is so upright.

32:33.700 --> 32:34.452
Indeed.

32:34.463 --> 32:35.420
As expected of Lord Qiu.

32:35.420 --> 32:36.270
How upright.

32:36.330 --> 32:37.170
Yes.

32:37.170 --> 32:38.290
Why does he speak like that?

32:38.860 --> 32:39.700
Isn't he saying

32:39.940 --> 32:41.666
that Qingque Sect
has shamed the Six Sects?

32:57.349 --> 32:58.769
The auspicious time of the memorial

32:58.980 --> 32:59.820
can't be delayed.

33:19.860 --> 33:20.700
They vanished.

33:25.570 --> 33:26.490
This is incredible.

33:29.140 --> 33:30.620
Qingque Sect is still the best.

33:30.860 --> 33:31.960
No wonder it's the top sect.

33:32.153 --> 33:33.143
Worthy of its reputation.

33:33.900 --> 33:34.980
Lord Qi is impressive.

33:41.140 --> 33:43.180
Your Beichen Way

33:43.700 --> 33:44.730
softens hardness.

33:45.086 --> 33:46.526
The greatest sound is almost silent.

33:46.810 --> 33:47.900
It has reached perfection.

33:48.330 --> 33:49.570
I respect it.

33:51.570 --> 33:52.730
Thank you for your praise.

33:55.530 --> 33:56.370
Everyone,

33:57.330 --> 33:58.490
in times of peace,

33:58.900 --> 33:59.900
with the world at ease,

34:00.730 --> 34:03.810
we honor the Founder

34:04.380 --> 34:08.130
and pay tribute to the spirit
of Founder Beichen.

34:08.780 --> 34:10.860
We hope all martial peers

34:11.490 --> 34:13.820
will join our Six Sects,

34:14.490 --> 34:16.260
uphold justice for the people,

34:16.820 --> 34:19.010
take the safety of the common folk
as our duty,

34:19.740 --> 34:20.960
and promote the righteous path.

34:21.490 --> 34:23.010
Promote the righteous path.

34:23.780 --> 34:25.210
Promote the righteous path.

34:31.090 --> 34:33.176
You're the one
who broke into the cellar last night.

34:33.780 --> 34:34.690
Who exactly are you?

34:38.090 --> 34:39.583
You are Cai Pingshu's niece, right?

34:40.980 --> 34:43.130
Why are you helping
these cold-blooded beasts?

34:45.130 --> 34:46.090
You know my aunt?

35:14.170 --> 35:15.210
Who are you?

35:15.900 --> 35:17.690
Why barge in here

35:17.780 --> 35:18.900
and ruin our memorial?

35:24.530 --> 35:25.370
Ms. Luo?

35:26.940 --> 35:27.780
Yuanrong.

35:30.570 --> 35:31.410
Yuanrong.

35:32.820 --> 35:33.660
Why are you here?

35:34.210 --> 35:35.820
I'm the disciple of Master Canghuan,

35:35.860 --> 35:37.210
former lord of Taichu Temple.

35:37.980 --> 35:38.900
Why shouldn't I come?

35:41.340 --> 35:42.180
Lord Qi,

35:42.540 --> 35:43.410
I came here because...

35:43.420 --> 35:44.260
Yuanrong,

35:52.760 --> 35:54.986
this is the 200th anniversary
of the Founder's passing.

35:55.570 --> 35:57.340
Such a solemn and serious day.

35:58.050 --> 35:59.210
If you act rashly,

36:00.980 --> 36:02.940
I'll have to kill you.

36:03.260 --> 36:04.100
Yuanfeng,

36:05.690 --> 36:06.926
Yuanrong may be stubborn,

36:06.937 --> 36:08.226
but she doesn't deserve to die.

36:08.300 --> 36:09.140
Silence.

36:12.940 --> 36:13.780
Yuanrong,

36:14.860 --> 36:16.340
for the sake of our shared fellowship,

36:17.210 --> 36:18.780
return with me to Taichu Temple.

36:20.050 --> 36:21.010
I won't harm you.

36:21.820 --> 36:22.660
Senior Qiu,

36:23.210 --> 36:24.530
Ms. Luo has managed to come here.

36:24.940 --> 36:26.226
Surely, she has an urgent matter.

36:27.050 --> 36:28.210
Why do you keep stopping her?

36:28.860 --> 36:30.300
This is within our sect.

36:30.860 --> 36:32.650
How can a junior speak now?

36:33.300 --> 36:34.940
Yuanrong was our childhood friend.

36:35.610 --> 36:36.820
She lost her beloved.

36:37.380 --> 36:38.820
It's not easy that she survived.

36:39.300 --> 36:40.260
She's here today;

36:40.780 --> 36:42.210
why not let her speak?

36:43.900 --> 36:44.780
Abbess Jingyuan,

36:46.260 --> 36:47.100
Lord Qi,

36:47.780 --> 36:50.210
I do not intend to cause trouble
on the memorial,

36:52.570 --> 36:54.530
but without everyone present,

36:55.980 --> 36:58.260
I fear my immense grievance
can't be voiced.

36:59.490 --> 37:01.740
Please, for my late master's sake,

37:03.210 --> 37:04.690
allow me to speak a few words.

37:04.940 --> 37:05.780
Luo Yuanrong,

37:07.226 --> 37:08.866
you've caused enough trouble
these years.

37:09.130 --> 37:10.980
Why not retreat now?

37:11.260 --> 37:12.100
Lord Qiu,

37:13.900 --> 37:14.860
it's reached this point.

37:15.260 --> 37:16.490
Rather than suppress it,

37:16.860 --> 37:18.860
it's better to reveal everything

37:19.490 --> 37:20.820
and clear the misunderstanding

37:21.130 --> 37:22.570
before the Founder's spirit.

37:24.490 --> 37:25.940
It truly is a misunderstanding.

37:27.940 --> 37:29.380
As you all know,

37:30.010 --> 37:31.740
Wu Yuanying of our sect

37:32.530 --> 37:34.780
died over ten years ago
in a battle with the demon sect.

37:36.260 --> 37:37.490
However,

37:38.090 --> 37:40.570
since then,

37:41.130 --> 37:43.420
Yuanrong could not let go,

37:43.740 --> 37:45.050
insisting he was still alive.

37:46.260 --> 37:48.380
For over ten years,
she's repeatedly pressured us

37:49.090 --> 37:50.900
to infiltrate the demon sect
to rescue him,

37:50.900 --> 37:52.130
or falsely claimed

37:52.130 --> 37:53.530
I killed Yuanying,

37:55.980 --> 37:57.530
wrongly accusing me.

37:58.010 --> 37:58.850
At that time,

37:59.490 --> 38:01.010
Master learned that the demon sect used

38:01.010 --> 38:02.556
living humans to create corpse slaves.

38:04.210 --> 38:05.650
He resolved to protect the people.

38:07.170 --> 38:08.490
He called martial heroes,

38:09.300 --> 38:10.260
split into groups,

38:10.613 --> 38:12.513
and went to the Hanhai Mountains
to fight evil.

38:13.780 --> 38:14.620
That day,

38:16.570 --> 38:18.490
everyone battled the demon sect.

38:19.940 --> 38:21.380
Yuanying and his team

38:22.380 --> 38:25.210
encountered Elder Kaiyang
of Nie Hengcheng.

38:26.210 --> 38:27.650
Knowing he could not win,

38:28.470 --> 38:29.900
- he shouted for retreat.
- Retreat!

38:29.980 --> 38:31.010
(Young Qiu Yuanfeng)

38:31.010 --> 38:33.530
But Qiu Yuanfeng, greedy for merit,

38:34.940 --> 38:36.530
recklessly attacked.

38:38.490 --> 38:39.860
Kaiyang was infuriated.

38:40.980 --> 38:42.210
Yuanying, disregarding danger,

38:42.210 --> 38:43.436
sacrificed himself to save him.

38:45.820 --> 38:46.740
- Run!
- Okay!

38:47.610 --> 38:50.010
Qiu Yuanfeng abandoned Yuanying

38:50.260 --> 38:51.340
and fled.

39:05.980 --> 39:06.820
Exactly.

39:07.570 --> 39:09.010
That day, Yuanying saved me.

39:10.380 --> 39:12.530
But I'm not cowardly.

39:13.690 --> 39:15.350
I only escaped

39:15.690 --> 39:16.530
by Yuanying's orders.

39:16.903 --> 39:18.260
When Yuanying told you to escape,

39:18.260 --> 39:19.420
you didn't.

39:19.630 --> 39:20.490
You caused trouble,

39:20.490 --> 39:22.090
provoked Kaiyang, and ran away?

39:22.380 --> 39:23.220
Lord Qiu,

39:23.650 --> 39:25.570
take responsibility
for the mess you caused.

39:26.490 --> 39:27.650
Running after causing havoc?

39:27.980 --> 39:29.210
Isn't that

39:29.210 --> 39:30.210
leaving Yuanying to die?

39:33.820 --> 39:34.900
I'll never forget

39:35.650 --> 39:36.820
the life-saving debt.

39:37.820 --> 39:38.660
But ultimately,

39:39.570 --> 39:41.260
we were all trying to defeat the demon.

39:42.570 --> 39:43.570
How am I wrong?

39:44.380 --> 39:45.490
Yuanying isn't dead!

39:45.490 --> 39:47.420
Your obsession

39:47.420 --> 39:48.980
has disrupted the sect.

39:49.420 --> 39:50.980
Yuanying is dead!

39:51.050 --> 39:52.650
Yuanying is alive.

40:00.170 --> 40:02.340
You are so stubborn.

40:05.860 --> 40:06.700
Fine.

40:07.490 --> 40:08.900
If what you say is true,

40:10.170 --> 40:12.260
produce convincing evidence.

40:29.340 --> 40:32.900
(Wu Xiong, Wu Gang, Taichu Temple)

41:30.980 --> 41:31.820
Yuanying,

41:36.380 --> 41:37.220
I'm Qi Yunke.

41:37.820 --> 41:38.660
Can you hear me?

41:44.610 --> 41:45.450
Yuanying!

41:48.690 --> 41:49.530
Yuanying!

41:55.420 --> 41:56.980
These demon sect beasts

41:56.980 --> 41:58.650
are worse than animals.

42:10.340 --> 42:11.380
Impossible.

42:13.340 --> 42:14.570
I saw him die

42:19.570 --> 42:20.740
with my own eyes.

42:25.650 --> 42:26.900
Where did you find him?

42:28.610 --> 42:30.296
You must've colluded
with the demon sect.

42:30.860 --> 42:31.700
You are right.

42:33.050 --> 42:34.380
I indeed entered the demon sect.

42:35.260 --> 42:36.420
Over a year ago,

42:37.010 --> 42:38.980
I once again clashed with Qiu Yuanfeng.

42:40.490 --> 42:41.650
Why didn't you save Yuanying?

42:41.940 --> 42:42.780
Let go!

42:42.820 --> 42:43.660
Tell me!

42:48.860 --> 42:49.820
Expel her.

42:50.420 --> 42:51.260
Yes.

42:52.210 --> 42:53.610
He severely injured me.

42:55.090 --> 42:56.690
Mr. Chang Haosheng saved me.

43:09.050 --> 43:09.890
Yuanrong?

44:12.340 --> 44:16.260
(Chang Fort)

44:27.260 --> 44:33.300
(Chang Fort)

45:48.090 --> 45:50.490
I disguised myself
as an ugly scavenger woman

45:52.090 --> 45:53.610
and searched every dungeon and prison

45:53.610 --> 45:55.570
along Youming Path

45:57.530 --> 45:59.010
for a whole year.

46:00.996 --> 46:02.300
Finally, in the EightClaw Prison,

46:02.300 --> 46:03.900
I found Yuanying.

46:19.340 --> 46:20.180
Yuanying!

46:23.210 --> 46:25.610
His eyes were gouged, his tongue cut,
and ligaments severed.

46:26.300 --> 46:27.300
He was soaked in poison.

46:31.820 --> 46:33.090
For over ten years,

46:35.490 --> 46:36.570
Yuanying lived

46:36.570 --> 46:38.170
a life worse than death,

46:39.740 --> 46:40.580
tormented little

46:40.860 --> 46:41.700
by little

46:42.570 --> 46:44.170
to this state.

46:45.740 --> 46:46.610
You knew all along?

46:49.490 --> 46:51.130
I did not know Yuanying was alive.

46:52.900 --> 46:53.740
Even if I did,

46:55.130 --> 46:57.130
returning would've been certain death.

47:00.420 --> 47:01.940
What could I do?

47:02.610 --> 47:03.610
Many

47:03.980 --> 47:05.490
survived the great battle.

47:07.530 --> 47:09.170
I tracked them down one by one,

47:10.050 --> 47:11.260
asked carefully

47:11.260 --> 47:12.170
and clearly.

47:13.860 --> 47:14.780
Qiu Yuanfeng,

47:15.650 --> 47:17.610
could you really not save Yuanying?

47:18.170 --> 47:19.940
You harbored resentment for him,

47:21.340 --> 47:22.780
thinking that as long as he lived,

47:23.570 --> 47:25.130
you'd have no chance to rise.

47:25.170 --> 47:26.820
So, you abandoned him.

47:27.430 --> 47:29.540
Everyone, don't let her fool you.

47:30.300 --> 47:31.690
Yuanying has been trapped

47:31.690 --> 47:33.820
in the demon sect's prison for years.

47:34.380 --> 47:36.130
How could he be rescued easily

47:36.340 --> 47:38.650
and happen to appear at the memorial?

47:39.340 --> 47:40.650
This is the demon sect's plot

47:41.800 --> 47:42.650
to slander me,

47:42.650 --> 47:43.570
sow discord,

47:43.570 --> 47:44.570
and divide our Six Sects.

47:45.090 --> 47:47.050
How evil their hearts are.

47:47.050 --> 47:47.890
Qiu Yuanfeng,

47:48.490 --> 47:50.260
do you still want to twist the truth?

47:51.490 --> 47:52.820
I only want to prevent Yuanying

47:53.490 --> 47:54.860
from being used by your demon sect.

48:15.650 --> 48:17.010
Watch out! It's Thunderstorm!

48:35.041 --> 48:45.701
=Generation to Generation=

49:04.461 --> 49:08.871
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

49:09.436 --> 49:14.051
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

49:14.391 --> 49:18.956
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

49:19.481 --> 49:23.781
♪Free to wander in the world♪

49:26.726 --> 49:31.426
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

49:31.951 --> 49:36.241
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

49:36.901 --> 49:40.931
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

49:41.246 --> 49:46.371
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

49:46.946 --> 49:51.756
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

49:51.971 --> 49:56.141
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

49:56.866 --> 50:00.801
♪I freely roam in the world♪

50:01.301 --> 50:06.576
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

50:29.306 --> 50:34.436
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

50:34.801 --> 50:39.171
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

50:39.436 --> 50:43.566
♪I freely roam in the world♪

50:43.751 --> 50:49.326
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
